headline: VoPay Expands Embedded Payments Offering with Real-Time PayPal and Venmo Payouts
summary: VANCOUVER, British Columbia, September 18, 2025--VoPay, a leading provider of Embedded Payments and Treasury-as-a-Service solutions, today announced an extension of its payment orchestration platform with real-time payouts to PayPal and Venmo. Effective immediately, businesses in North America can send funds directly to PayPal and Venmo accounts, unlocking faster, more flexible, and highly inclusive payout options.
